The paper deals with image processing and computer vision techniques to transfer the style of a headshot photo to face images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of Markov Random Fields (MRF) for establishing patch correspondences, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). Additionally, the paper involves the use of Laplacian stacks, which is a common technique in multimedia processing and falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves the use of post-processing techniques to remove artifacts, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
